<P>
RECYCLING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It is interesting to note that a country so advanced in technology is so behind 
in such practical matters as recycling. We can no longer afford to close our 
eyes to a problem of this magnitude. 
</P>
<P>
Thank you for addressing this issue (Part I, June 3). In the meantime I will 
continue to use cloth diapers to rid myself of a guilty conscience. 
</P>
<P>
ELIZABETH BAKKER 
</P>
<P>
Lakewood 
</P>
