<P>
Nicaragua has sent several planeloads of Soviet Bloc weapons to Panama in 
recent months to help strongman Manuel A. Noriega prepare his forces for any 
U.S. military attack, according to Sandinista military and non-diplomatic U.S. 
sources in Managua. The shipments included dozens of AK-47 assault rifles, 
