<P>
Eastern Seeks Pilots' Concessions: Eastern Airlines is asking its striking 
pilots for $20 million in wage and benefits concessions as part of its 
restructuring plan, a company spokesman said. The pilots, members of the Air 
Line Pilots Assn., who are striking in sympathy with Eastern's machinists, 
