county all-star game June 25 in UC Irvine's Bren Center. 
</P>
<P>
Lakers guard Michael Cooper and former California Coach Pete Newell also will 
make appearances at the dinner. Tickets, priced at $26, can be reserved by 
calling Vern Vegso at 642-3075. 
