</P>
<P>
Pacific Coast Highway and Warner Avenue 
</P>
<P>
Pacific Coast Highway and Lake Street 
</P>
<P>
Hamilton and Magnolia avenues 
</P>
<P>
32nd Street and Balboa Boulevard 
</P>
<P>
Fashion Island 
</P>
<P>
Laguna Beach Bus Station 
</P>
<P>
Coast Highway and Crown Valley Parkway 
</P>
<P>
Coast Highway and Del Obispo Street 
</P>
<P>
K mart Plaza 
</P>
<P>
25 Fullerton to Huntington Beach via Knott Avenue and Golden West Street 
</P>
<P>
STOPS 
</P>
<P>
Nutwood and Commonwealth avenues 
</P>
<P>
Chapman Avenue and Lemon Street 
</P>
<P>
Hughes Aircraft Co. 
</P>
<P>
Gilbert Street and Malvern Avenue 
</P>
<P>
Fullerton Park-N-Ride 
</P>
<P>
Beach and Artesia boulevards 
</P>
<P>
La Palma and Knott avenues 
</P>
<P>
Knott and Katella avenues 
</P>
<P>
Golden West Street and Westminster Avenue 
</P>
<P>
Westminster Mall 
</P>
<P>
Edinger Avenue and Gothard Street 
</P>
<P>
Yorktown Avenue and Main Street 
</P>
<P>
Pacific Coast Highway and Lake Street 
</P>
